{"tid":2160841,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"有奶共派燈神之稱既劉兆佳指：美國不會動用涉及金融的「核子手段」，俞懷松：新一輪制裁包括港交所 （388）","createTime":"2020-08-17T08:27:47.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-19T17:32:43.000Z","uid":230104,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"c6f8cff190f3dda7f164cbf838d08745fa16ad0c","tid":2160841,"uid":230104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T08:27:47.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200817/5KZKFVJW6ZDZFM3HMHJ4TUIODU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200817%2F5KZKFVJW6ZDZFM3HMHJ4TUIODU%2F&d=F9sYfJh4wRYjdPScc1OpRlLn0p5rLcPQxw7X33U7JQw%3D&h=70598373\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200817%2F5KZKFVJW6ZDZFM3HMHJ4TUIODU%2F&h=442f1b37\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200817/5KZKFVJW6ZDZFM3HMHJ4TUIODU/</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n全國港澳研究會副會長劉兆佳早前指，認為美國不希望付出大代價又可表達不滿，相信美國不會動用涉及金融的「核子手段」；近期就陸續傳出，在港的中資銀行已紛紛採取措施遵守美國制裁命令，從而保障他們涉及的美元融資渠道及相關海外網絡。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n被視為有份參與推動制裁的美國共和黨海外事務組織副主席俞懷松（Solomon Yue），日前就在Twitter指，最新一輪制裁將很快來臨，更點名港交所 （388） 將成為受害者；加上美國總統特朗普上周以「go to hell」（去死）批評香港金融中心在中國控制之下的未來，令外界猜測是暗示下一波制裁或牽涉包括香港的企業，因而「連累」港交所。"},{"pid":"79f881f43bd6199b2b12c53b6788fb56c009c9d1","tid":2160841,"uid":2419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T08:30:34.000Z","msg":"都唔知係咪真係有呢個人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"776fdfb61b9fb05ee9b12474e0e5d7176e7cd023","tid":2160841,"uid":134474,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"79f881f43bd6199b2b12c53b6788fb56c009c9d1","tid":2160841,"uid":2419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T08:30:34.000Z","msg":"都唔知係咪真係有呢個人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T08:32:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wFDPB7b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwFDPB7b.jpg&h=ce7e6fc0&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0dc97c1eb800ec554f6f797ef5f8025ad545bc9e","tid":2160841,"uid":230104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T08:44:06.000Z","msg":"劉兆佳條傻仔講親都燈，做老董痣囊時，害撚到老董落台<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2888b27baa062a571e98af08e5416e0d894d01b9","tid":2160841,"uid":230104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-19T17:17:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"77a388474b721b82f4b56e99b7e3380f1641cca3","tid":2160841,"uid":113000,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-19T17:23:15.000Z","msg":"劉兆佳2020年仲停留係公公猜想主子心態<br />\n<br />\n好撚嘔心"},{"pid":"a51ec262595675f42d1b203d27fa31b3120f3b25","tid":2160841,"uid":26770,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"77a388474b721b82f4b56e99b7e3380f1641cca3","tid":2160841,"uid":113000,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-19T17:23:15.000Z","msg":"劉兆佳2020年仲停留係公公猜想主子心態<br />\n<br />\n好撚嘔心"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-19T17:32:43.000Z","msg":"劉兆佳的研究/教育成就接近零<br />\n<br />\n因為係第一批奶共的知識份子所以中共狂升呢條友官<br />\n<br />\n呢條友係專業的公公"}]}